'''TEOTWAWKI''' is an [[acronym]] standing for "'''T'''he '''E'''nd '''O'''f '''T'''he '''W'''orld '''A'''s '''W'''e '''K'''now '''I'''t". The acronym is spoken “Tee-ought-walk-ee”. It is used often online by members of [[Survivalism|survivalist]] groups, but has spread into common usage, even making an appearance in lyrics by [[R.E.M. (band)|R.E.M.]].

